How to Get Hired Faster in India
üîπ 1. Build Real Projects
Deploy smart contracts on testnets and link them in your portfolio. Practical work matters more than certificates.
üîπ 2. Focus on Security Skills
Understanding vulnerabilities (reentrancy, gas optimization) is a huge advantage ‚Äî companies pay more for secure devs.
üîπ 3. Learn Supporting Tools
Hardhat, Truffle, Foundry ‚Äî these make you more efficient than just knowing Solidity.
üîπ 4. Network Actively
‚Ä¢	LinkedIn
‚Ä¢	GitHub
‚Ä¢	Web3 communities & hackathons
Connections often lead to job referrals.
üîπ 5. Freelance or Internship First
Sites like Upwork or Toptal help you get initial experience and visibility. 
