üìå Example Documentation Snippet
Blockchain Developers at Wipro, Infosys, and Accenture are expected to have strong understanding of distributed ledger technologies (e.g., Ethereum, Hyperledger, Corda), backend programming (Java/Node.js), and the software development lifecycle. Mid to senior roles require experience with smart contract design, cloud platforms, security protocols, and enterprise integration practices. Architect/Consultant roles add solution design, compliance, and stakeholder leadership responsibilities.

